JULIA ROBERTS, FOUR.

28:49.128 --> 28:51.097
- THANK YOU.

28:51.130 --> 28:53.499
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN.

28:53.532 --> 28:55.968
WHEN A MAN GIVES YOU A RING,
IT'S SPECIAL.

28:56.002 --> 28:57.369
