28:57.403 --> 28:59.906
- WELL, I WOULDN'T KNOW.

29:02.341 --> 29:04.877
- THEN MAYBE IT'S TIME
YOU FOUND OUT.

29:04.911 --> 29:06.813
- FOUND OUT WHAT?

29:10.817 --> 29:13.786
- MICHAEL NOVOTNY...

29:13.820 --> 29:17.756
YOU ARE THE MAN I'VE BEEN
LOOKING FOR ALL MY LIFE.

29:21.227 --> 29:25.164
I AM SO VERY BLESSED
TO HAVE FOUND YOU.

29:28.567 --> 29:30.569
WHICH IS WHY I'M ASKING YOU...

29:30.602 --> 29:35.074
