FOR SCORING HIS FIRST FILM.

30:49.648 --> 30:51.617
- YOUR HOUSE IS AMAZING.

30:51.650 --> 30:56.956
- YEAH. I CALL IT THE HOUSE
THAT V MEN BUILT.

30:56.989 --> 30:59.425
SOON YOU'LL HAVE A HOUSE
THAT RAGE BUILT.

30:59.458 --> 31:02.962
