31:19.946 --> 31:21.180
- GREAT, BRETT.

31:21.213 --> 31:26.919
- NOW, LET'S GET YOU A DRINK.

31:26.953 --> 31:29.922
THE MEETING'S ALL SET
FOR THURSDAY AT THE STUDIO.

31:29.956 --> 31:32.324
