- THANKS.

32:03.089 --> 32:05.024
- WHAT WOULD YOU THINK
OF CON FOR RAGE?

32:05.057 --> 32:08.627
- HE...
I MEAN, YOU WOULD BE WONDERFUL.

32:08.660 --> 32:11.630
- GET ME A SCRIPT
WHEN YOU HAVE IT.

32:18.004 --> 32:23.109
[indistinct chatter]

32:23.142 --> 32:24.977
