33:29.441 --> 33:30.776
- HEY, HERE'S MOOSIE'S.

33:30.809 --> 33:32.511
- GOOD. LET'S GO IN HERE
AND GET WARM.

33:32.544 --> 33:34.046
- FIRST ROUND'S ON ME.
- WAIT.

33:34.080 --> 33:35.514
- YOU'LL HAVE A CANADA DRY.

33:35.547 --> 33:37.716
- AND IF ANYONE ASKS YOU
HOW OLD YOU ARE...

33:37.749 --> 33:39.251
- I'LL JUST SAY
WHAT I USED TO SAY:

33:39.285 --> 33:41.153
"HOW OLD WOULD YOU
LIKE ME TO BE?"

33:41.187 --> 33:43.189
- GOMORRAH IS
RIGHT ACROSS THE STREET.

33:43.222 --> 33:44.590
WE'LL GO THERE LATER
AFTER WE'VE BEEN HERE.

33:44.623 --> 33:47.159
- OKAY. COME ON.

33:51.563 --> 33:55.201
- THANKS.

33:55.234 --> 33:56.602
- I DON'T KNOW ABOUT YOU,

33:56.635 --> 33:59.205
