- YOU TOO?

33:59.238 --> 34:00.472
- MAKE IT THREE.

34:00.506 --> 34:02.241
- IT REALLY REMINDS ME OF...

34:02.274 --> 34:03.275
all: WOODY'S.

34:03.309 --> 34:04.543
- YEAH.
- YES.

34:04.576 --> 34:05.844
- AND THE STRANGEST THING
OF ALL IS

34:05.877 --> 34:08.280
