TO WALK IN.

34:08.314 --> 34:10.549
- UH, MOLSON'S.

34:10.582 --> 34:12.351
- BRIAN!

34:12.384 --> 34:13.552
- CALM DOWN.
- HEY!

34:13.585 --> 34:15.821
- KEEP YOUR PANTS ON,
OR NOT.

34:15.854 --> 34:17.556
- HOW DID YOU GET HERE?

34:17.589 --> 34:20.092
- MIKEY, DID NO ONE
EVER TELL YOU?

34:20.126 --> 34:22.561
IN 1903, AT KITTY HAWK
IN NORTH CAROLINA,

34:22.594 --> 34:25.697
THE WRIGHT BROTHERS INVENTED
THIS THING CALLED FLIGHT.

34:25.731 --> 34:27.166
- FLIGHT.
- RIGHT.

34:27.199 --> 34:28.567
- WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

34:28.600 --> 34:31.337
- THE LIBERTY RIDE BEGINS HERE,
AM I CORRECT?

34:31.370 --> 34:32.871
- SO YOU CAME TO CHEER US ON?

34:32.904 --> 34:33.872
- EXACTLY, PROFESSOR.

34:33.905 --> 34:35.874
I CASHED IN 25,000 TRAVEL MILES

34:35.907 --> 34:37.709
SO I COULD COME HERE
AND BE YOUR CHEERLEADER.

34:37.743 --> 34:39.478
NO. I'M GOING ON THE RIDE.

34:39.511 --> 34:42.181
I'LL BE BUSTING A NUT
FOR CHARITY, SAME AS YOU.

34:42.214 --> 34:45.217
- THE NATIVES ARE SO FRIENDLY.

34:45.251 --> 34:46.885
THIS IS JEAN-CLAUDE.

34:46.918 --> 34:49.455
HE'S FRENCH-CANADIAN.

34:49.488 --> 34:50.722
- BONSOIR.

34:50.756 --> 34:53.259
- HI. BONSOIR.
- BONSOIR.

34:53.292 --> 34:55.327
DON'T YOU JUST LOVE IT?

34:55.361 --> 34:56.895
