[clears throat]

35:04.370 --> 35:06.372
SORRY, JEAN-CLAUDE, UM,

35:06.405 --> 35:08.374
BUT, UH, AS MUCH AS
I WOULD LOVE FOR YOU TO,

35:08.407 --> 35:10.609
