YOU'RE GOING TO MAKE IT.

36:31.323 --> 36:34.326
- OH, I MIGHT JUST SURPRISE YOU.

36:34.360 --> 36:37.996
- THANKS, BUT I'VE HAD
ENOUGH SURPRISES.

36:38.029 --> 36:42.434
BEN PROPOSED.

36:42.468 --> 36:45.471
- PROPOSED WHAT?
- MARRIAGE.

36:45.504 --> 36:48.574
IT'S LEGAL FOR US TO
GET MARRIED HERE IN TORONTO.

36:48.607 --> 36:52.844
- I BELIEVE I READ THAT
SOMEWHERE.

36:52.878 --> 36:54.880
WELL, I HOPE WHILE HE WAS
DOWN ON HIS KNEES,

36:54.913 --> 36:56.982
HE DID SOMETHING USEFUL.

36:57.015 --> 36:59.351
- IT WAS BEAUTIFUL
AND HEARTFELT.

36:59.385 --> 37:02.454
- I'M SURE.

37:02.488 --> 37:04.323
BUT YOU DECLINED, OF COURSE,

37:04.356 --> 37:06.492
BECAUSE DEEP DOWN,
YOU STILL LOVE ME BEST.

37:06.525 --> 37:11.330
- SHUT UP.

37:11.363 --> 37:15.367
I DIDN'T GIVE HIM
AN ANSWER YET.

37:15.401 --> 37:17.002
- WELL, WHAT'S STOPPING YOU?

37:17.035 --> 37:19.338
BESIDES THE FACT THAT
IT'S THE MOST PATHETIC IDEA

37:19.371 --> 37:20.739
I'VE EVER HEARD?
- IT JUST SO HAPPENS

37:20.772 --> 37:22.408
THAT A LOT OF GAY MEN
WANT TO GET MARRIED.

37:22.441 --> 37:25.344
- DARLING, HAVE YOU SEEN THEM?

37:25.377 --> 37:26.878
AND SINCE WHEN DID YOU EVER

37:26.912 --> 37:29.348
HAVE THE LEAST INTEREST
IN GETTING MARRIED?

37:29.381 --> 37:32.484
- I DIDN'T. BUT NOT
BECAUSE I DIDN'T WANT TO,

37:32.518 --> 37:34.953
BUT BECAUSE I NEVER THOUGHT
I COULD.

37:34.986 --> 37:38.490
IT WASN'T A STORY I TOLD MYSELF
LIKE STRAIGHT KIDS DID,

37:38.524 --> 37:41.059
YOU KNOW, THAT SOME DAY I'D MEET
THAT SPECIAL PERSON,

37:41.092 --> 37:44.062
AND WE'D FALL IN LOVE
AND HAVE A BIG WEDDING.

37:44.095 --> 37:47.065
IT--IT WAS NEVER REAL FOR ME.

37:47.098 --> 37:48.900
AND THEN ALL THIS STUFF
STARTED HAPPENING,

37:48.934 --> 37:51.036
IN MASSACHUSETTS
AND CALIFORNIA AND HERE.

37:51.069 --> 37:53.372
- ALL OF A SUDDEN,
A WHOLE, WIDE WORLD

37:53.405 --> 37:57.075
OF WONDERFUL OPPORTUNITIES
OPENED UP.

37:57.108 --> 38:00.512
VOWS AND RICE AND
REGISTERING AT POTTERY BARN.

38:00.546 --> 38:02.914
NOT TO MENTION
AN ACRIMONIOUS DIVORCE,

38:02.948 --> 38:07.052
AN UGLY SETTLEMENT,
AND HAVING YOUR KID HATE YOU.

38:07.085 --> 38:09.087
LOOK, LISTEN TO ME.

38:09.120 --> 38:11.790
ARE YOU LISTENING?
- I'M LISTENING.

38:11.823 --> 38:16.995
- WE'RE QUEER.
WE DON'T NEED MARRIAGE.

38:17.028 --> 38:20.098
WE DON'T NEED THE SANCTION
OF DICKLESS POLITICIANS

38:20.131 --> 38:23.101
AND PEDERAST PRIESTS.

38:23.134 --> 38:25.704
