38:27.473 --> 38:29.007
- BUT IT'S ALSO
OUR GOD-GIVEN RIGHT

38:29.040 --> 38:32.578
TO HAVE EVERYTHING
THAT STRAIGHT PEOPLE HAVE.

38:32.611 --> 38:37.583
BECAUSE WE'RE EVERY BIT
AS MUCH HUMAN AS THEY ARE.

38:47.859 --> 38:52.698
- WELL, YOU'RE A WRITER.

38:52.731 --> 38:56.334
REWRITE THE STORY.

39:00.772 --> 39:04.876
[cheering]

39:07.178 --> 39:09.681
- CONGRATULATIONS.

39:14.486 --> 39:18.023
- HMM. THIS IS TOUCHING,
DON'T YOU THINK?

39:19.625 --> 39:21.893
- I DO.

39:24.630 --> 39:27.065
I DO.

39:29.067 --> 39:30.736
BEN, DID YOU HEAR
WHAT I JUST SAID?

39:30.769 --> 39:34.673
- YEAH, I HEARD YOU.
