TO BUILD GAYOPOLIS.

39:52.558 --> 39:55.026
- THERE ARE A FEW OTHER PICTURES
WE'D LIKE TO SHOOT HERE.

39:55.060 --> 39:56.828
- THIS IS THE ONLY ONE
THAT I'M DIRECTING.

39:56.862 --> 39:58.664
[chuckles]
YA PUNK.

39:58.697 --> 40:00.432
