MADE YOU 250 MILLION.

40:12.077 --> 40:13.845
- YEAH. THIS ONE'S DIFFERENT.

40:13.879 --> 40:16.915
A GAY SUPERHERO?
- THE WORLD'S READY FOR IT.

40:16.948 --> 40:18.917
- MAYBE YOUR WORLD,
BUT NOT TOPEKA.

40:18.950 --> 40:21.219
- IF IT'S GOOD,
IF IT'S GOT A BIG ENOUGH STAR,

40:21.252 --> 40:24.222
IF YOU HYPE THE SHIT OUT OF IT,
THEY'LL GO.

40:24.255 --> 40:26.057
RIGHT?

40:26.091 --> 40:27.959
GUYS?

40:27.993 --> 40:30.962
- IT ALL LOOKS PRETTY GRIM
AND DEPRESSING TO ME.

40:30.996 --> 40:33.064
WHO WANTS TO SEE A KID
GET HIS HEAD BASHED IN?

40:33.098 --> 40:34.800
AND WHAT ABOUT ALL THIS SEX?

40:34.833 --> 40:37.603
BLOWJOBS AND BUTT-FUCKING
ON EVERY PAGE.

40:37.636 --> 40:40.539
- IT'S SOMETHING THE AUDIENCE
HAS NEVER SEEN BEFORE.

40:40.572 --> 40:43.675
- WHAT MAKES YOU THINK
THEY WANT TO SEE IT NOW?

40:43.709 --> 40:45.611
