BE SO FUCKING ARROGANT?

41:00.125 --> 41:03.094
- EXCUSE ME, MR. FENDERMAN,
BUT OUR COMIC BOOK

41:03.128 --> 41:05.030
WAS CONCEIVED THAT WAY
FOR A REASON.

41:05.063 --> 41:09.635
BECAUSE A LOT OF THE SHIT THAT
GAY PEOPLE GO THROUGH IS GRIM.

41:09.668 --> 41:11.903
I OUGHT TO KNOW, I'M A KID WHO
GOT HIS HEAD BASHED IN.

41:11.937 --> 41:14.239
AS FAR AS "THE ASS BUSINESS,"

41:14.272 --> 41:17.008
GETTING YOUR BUTT FUCKED
IS ONE OF THE GREAT PLEASURES

41:17.042 --> 41:18.877
AND PRIVILEGES OF BEING GAY.

41:18.910 --> 41:21.847
IF YOU HAVEN'T EXPERIENCED IT
YOURSELF, I RECOMMEND IT.

41:21.880 --> 41:24.583
AS FAR AS RAGE IS CONCERNED,

41:24.616 --> 41:26.718
JUST BECAUSE HE HAS
NO APOLOGIES FOR WHO HE IS

41:26.752 --> 41:29.588
AND NO REGRETS ABOUT HIS LIFE
DOESN'T MAKE HIM ARROGANT.

41:29.621 --> 41:33.525
IT MAKES HIM HONEST AND BRAVE.

41:33.559 --> 41:35.527
SO DESPITE YOUR CONCERNS,

41:35.561 --> 41:38.263
WE PREFER TO BE TRUE TO
OUR ORIGINAL VISION.

41:38.296 --> 41:41.499
