ANYTHING LESS.

41:47.839 --> 41:50.075
- WE ARE HERE TODAY TO JOIN
IN MATRIMONY

41:50.108 --> 41:51.610
MR. MICHAEL NOVOTNY

41:51.643 --> 41:53.945
AND MR. BENJAMIN BRUCKNER.

41:53.979 --> 41:55.947
- [sniffling]
- CHRIST.

41:55.981 --> 41:57.549
