I'M GOING TO A WEDDING

41:57.583 --> 42:00.786
WITH TWO QUEENS.

42:00.819 --> 42:03.154
- DO YOU, MICHAEL,
PROMISE TO LOVE,

42:03.188 --> 42:05.891
RESPECT, AND CHERISH BEN,

42:05.924 --> 42:08.727
AND BE HIS TRUE
AND FAITHFUL HUSBAND?

42:11.930 --> 42:14.633
- I DO.

42:14.666 --> 42:18.303
- AND DO YOU, BEN,
PROMISE TO LOVE, RESPECT,

42:18.336 --> 42:19.771
AND CHERISH MICHAEL,

42:19.805 --> 42:24.209
AND BE HIS TRUE
AND FAITHFUL HUSBAND?

42:24.242 --> 42:25.777
