42:32.884 --> 42:34.653
- IF ANYONE KNOWS
OF ANY REASON

42:34.686 --> 42:37.255
WHY THESE TWO PEOPLE SHOULD NOT
BE JOINED IN MARRIAGE,

42:37.288 --> 42:40.225
SPEAK NOW
OR FOREVER HOLD YOUR PEACE.

42:41.693 --> 42:43.194
- YOU SAY ONE WORD,

42:43.228 --> 42:45.230
YOU'RE GONNA BE HOLDING
MORE THAN YOUR PEACE.

42:48.634 --> 42:52.337
- THE RINGS, PLEASE.

42:52.370 --> 42:55.040
- THANK YOU.

43:11.990 --> 43:15.026
- NOW, BY THE AUTHORITY
OF THE PROVINCE OF ONTARIO,

43:15.060 --> 43:17.929
